{"tid":1923900,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美財長努勤：IMF與世銀資金不會被用來償還中國債務","createTime":"2020-03-13T10:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T15:06:32.000Z","uid":141151,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8ed1a1054f2f8dcabf6bdb304d91e1fc994ba5db","tid":1923900,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T10:38:46.000Z","msg":"美財長努勤：IMF與世銀資金不會用來償還中國債務<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3098328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3098328&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=021b7a1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3098328&h=abe03a0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3098328</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國財政部長努勤（Steven Mnuchin）週三表示，針對中國「一帶一路」計畫，美國正與國際貨幣基金組織（IMF）及世界銀行（World Bank）合作，弄清楚該項目下各國的債務狀況，確保IMF及世銀向參與國提供的資金，不會被用來向中國還債。<br />\n《路透》報導，努勤於眾議院撥款委員會聽證會上表示：「我們認為這點至關重要。」「我們從沒打算讓這些國際組職（IMF及世銀）的錢，被用來向中國還債。」<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，一些國家因參與「一帶一路」計畫而背上債務，如巴基斯坦，已向IMF尋求協助。據報導，巴基斯坦在去年7月與IMF簽署1項60億美元的貸款計畫。<br />\n<br />\n但週四在北京舉辦的記者會上，中國外交部發言人耿爽對努勤的質疑做出回應，稱國際金融機構不是「政治工具」，並給予「一帶一路」倡議正面評價。"},{"pid":"55b9b9a2fca23990ba106fd66b4bc36d7c4fc6c1","tid":1923900,"uid":44358,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T10:48:55.000Z","msg":"全面封殺中蟈美金來源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家港股開始爆跌，中蟈廢企 cap 水大計準備玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26c1fd121e49ce4d7711b75ba27afc559d59f9c","tid":1923900,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56aa07e9ca838282e3b